{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"So, what I'd like to talk about is something"},{"time":5000,"text":"that was very dear to Kahn's heart, which is:"},{"time":7000,"text":"how do we discover what is really particular about a project?"},{"time":10000,"text":"How do you discover the uniqueness of a project as unique as a person?"},{"time":16000,"text":"Because it seems to me that finding this uniqueness"},{"time":19000,"text":"has to do with dealing with the whole force of globalization;"},{"time":29000,"text":"that the particular is central to finding the uniqueness of place"},{"time":35000,"text":"and the uniqueness of a program in a building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"And so I'll take you to Wichita, Kansas,"},{"time":42000,"text":"where I was asked some years ago to do a science museum"},{"time":45000,"text":"on a site, right downtown by the river."},{"time":50000,"text":"And I thought the secret of the site was to make the building of the river, part of the river."},{"time":56000,"text":"Unfortunately, though, the site was separated from the river by McLean Boulevard"},{"time":61000,"text":"so I suggested, \"Let's reroute McLean,\""},{"time":64000,"text":"and that gave birth instantly to Friends of McLean Boulevard."},{"time":68000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":73000,"text":"And it took six months to reroute it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76000,"text":"The first image I showed the building committee was"},{"time":82000,"text":"this astronomic observatory of Jantar Mantar in Jaipur"},{"time":87000,"text":"because I talked about what makes a building a building of science."},{"time":93000,"text":"And it seemed to me that this structure -- complex, rich and yet"},{"time":99000,"text":"totally rational: it's an instrument -- had something to do with science,"},{"time":102000,"text":"and somehow a building for science should be different and unique and speak of that."},{"time":107000,"text":"And so my first sketch after I left was to say,"},{"time":109000,"text":"\"Let's cut the channel and make an island and make an island building.\""},{"time":115000,"text":"And I got all excited and came back, and"},{"time":118000,"text":"they sort of looked at me in dismay and said, \"An island?"},{"time":121000,"text":"This used to be an island -- Ackerman Island --"},{"time":123000,"text":"and we filled in the channel during the Depression to create jobs.\""},{"time":126000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"And so the process began and they said,"},{"time":132000,"text":"\"You can't put it all on an island;"},{"time":134000,"text":"some of it has to be on the mainland because"},{"time":136000,"text":"we don't want to turn our back to the community.\""},{"time":139000,"text":"And there emerged a design: the galleries sort of forming an island"},{"time":143000,"text":"and you could walk through them or on the roof."},{"time":146000,"text":"And there were all kinds of exciting features:"},{"time":149000,"text":"you could come in through the landside buildings,"},{"time":152000,"text":"walk through the galleries into playgrounds in the landscape."},{"time":155000,"text":"If you were cheap you could walk on top of a bridge to the roof,"},{"time":158000,"text":"peek in the exhibits and then get totally seduced,"},{"time":162000,"text":"come back and pay the five dollars admission."},{"time":164000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":166000,"text":"And the client was happy -- well, sort of happy"},{"time":168000,"text":"because we were four million dollars over the budget, but essentially happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"But I was still troubled, and I was troubled because I felt this was capricious."},{"time":178000,"text":"It was complex, but there was something capricious about its complexity."},{"time":183000,"text":"It was, what I would say, compositional complexity,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and I felt that if I had to fulfill what I talked about --"},{"time":191000,"text":"a building for science -- there had to be some kind of a generating idea,"},{"time":194000,"text":"some kind of a generating geometry."},{"time":197000,"text":"And this gave birth to the idea of having toroidal generating geometry,"},{"time":202000,"text":"one with its center deep in the earth for the landside building"},{"time":206000,"text":"and a toroid with its center in the sky for the island building."},{"time":212000,"text":"A toroid, for those who don't know,"},{"time":214000,"text":"is the surface of a doughnut or, for some of us, a bagel."},{"time":218000,"text":"And out of this idea started spinning off many,"},{"time":222000,"text":"many kinds of variations of different plans and possibilities,"},{"time":227000,"text":"and then the plan itself evolved in relationship to the exhibits,"},{"time":231000,"text":"and you see the intersection of the plan with the toroidal geometry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"And finally the building -- this is the model."},{"time":240000,"text":"And when there were complaints about budget, I said,"},{"time":242000,"text":"\"Well, it's worth doing the island because you get twice for your money: reflections.\""},{"time":248000,"text":"And here's the building as it opened,"},{"time":251000,"text":"with a channel overlooking downtown, and as seen from downtown."},{"time":256000,"text":"And the bike route's going right through the building,"},{"time":259000,"text":"so those traveling the river would see the exhibits and be drawn to the building."},{"time":268000,"text":"The toroidal geometry made for a very efficient building:"},{"time":271000,"text":"every beam in this building is the same radius, all laminated wood."},{"time":276000,"text":"Every wall, every concrete wall is resisting the stresses and supporting the building."},{"time":282000,"text":"Every piece of the building works."},{"time":285000,"text":"These are the galleries with the light coming in through the skylights,"},{"time":290000,"text":"and at night, and on opening day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296000,"text":"Going back to 1976."},{"time":299000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":304000,"text":"In 1976, I was asked to design a children's memorial museum"},{"time":309000,"text":"in a Holocaust museum in Yad Vashem in Jerusalem,"},{"time":313000,"text":"which you see here the campus."},{"time":316000,"text":"I was asked to do a building,"},{"time":318000,"text":"and I was given all the artifacts of clothing and drawings."},{"time":324000,"text":"And I felt very troubled."},{"time":326000,"text":"I worked on it for months and I couldn't deal with it"},{"time":328000,"text":"because I felt people were coming out of the historic museum,"},{"time":331000,"text":"they are totally saturated with information"},{"time":334000,"text":"and to see yet another museum with information,"},{"time":337000,"text":"it would make them just unable to digest."},{"time":341000,"text":"And so I made a counter-proposal:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"I said, \"No building.\" There was a cave on the site; we tunnel into the hill,"},{"time":350000,"text":"descend through the rock into an underground chamber."},{"time":356000,"text":"There's an anteroom with photographs of children who perished"},{"time":360000,"text":"and then you come into a large space."},{"time":364000,"text":"There is a single candle flickering in the center;"},{"time":368000,"text":"by an arrangement of reflective glasses, it reflects into infinity in all directions."},{"time":375000,"text":"You walk through the space, a voice reads the names,"},{"time":380000,"text":"ages and place of birth of the children."},{"time":382000,"text":"This voice does not repeat for six months."},{"time":385000,"text":"And then you descend to light and to the north and to life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390000,"text":"Well, they said, \"People won't understand,"},{"time":392000,"text":"they'll think it's a discotheque. You can't do that.\""},{"time":394000,"text":"And they shelved the project. And it sat there for 10 years,"},{"time":398000,"text":"and then one day Abe Spiegel from Los Angeles,"},{"time":402000,"text":"who had lost his three-year-old son at Auschwitz,"},{"time":405000,"text":"came, saw the model, wrote the check and it got built 10 years later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"So, many years after that in 1998,"},{"time":415000,"text":"I was on one of my monthly trips to Jerusalem"},{"time":419000,"text":"and I got a call from the foreign ministry saying,"},{"time":422000,"text":"\"We've got the Chief Minister of the Punjab here."},{"time":428000,"text":"He is on a state visit. We took him on a visit to Yad Vashem,"},{"time":434000,"text":"we took him to the children's memorial; he was extremely moved."},{"time":437000,"text":"He's demanding to meet the architect. Could you come down and meet him in Tel Aviv?\""},{"time":440000,"text":"And I went down and Chief Minister Badal said to me,"},{"time":445000,"text":"\"We Sikhs have suffered a great deal, as you have Jews."},{"time":450000,"text":"I was very moved by what I saw today."},{"time":453000,"text":"We are going to build our national museum to tell the story of our people;"},{"time":457000,"text":"we're about to embark on that."},{"time":459000,"text":"I'd like you to come and design it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":461000,"text":"And so, you know, it's one of those things that you don't take too seriously."},{"time":467000,"text":"But two weeks later, I was in this little town, Anandpur Sahib,"},{"time":472000,"text":"outside Chandigarh, the capital of the Punjab,"},{"time":476000,"text":"and the temple and also next to it the fortress"},{"time":481000,"text":"that the last guru of the Sikhs, Guru Gobind, died in"},{"time":486000,"text":"as he wrote the Khalsa, which is their holy scripture."},{"time":491000,"text":"And I got to work and they took me somewhere down there,"},{"time":496000,"text":"nine kilometers away from the town and the temple,"},{"time":498000,"text":"and said, \"That's where we have chosen the location.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"And I said, \"This just doesn't make any sense."},{"time":505000,"text":"The pilgrims come here by the hundreds of thousands --"},{"time":508000,"text":"they're not going to get in trucks and buses and go down there."},{"time":511000,"text":"Let's get back to the town and walk to the site.\""},{"time":514000,"text":"And I recommended they do it right there, on that hill"},{"time":517000,"text":"and this hill, and bridge all the way into the town."},{"time":521000,"text":"And, as things are a little easier in India, the site was purchased within a week"},{"time":527000,"text":"and we were working."},{"time":529000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":530000,"text":"And my proposal was to split the museum into two --"},{"time":534000,"text":"the permanent exhibits at one end, the auditorium, library,"},{"time":539000,"text":"and changing exhibitions on the other --"},{"time":541000,"text":"to flood the valley into a series of water gardens"},{"time":545000,"text":"and to link it all to the fort and to the downtown."},{"time":549000,"text":"And the structures rise from the sand cliffs --"},{"time":553000,"text":"they're built in concrete and sandstones; the roofs are stainless steel --"},{"time":558000,"text":"they are facing south and reflecting light towards the temple itself,"},{"time":563000,"text":"pedestrians crisscross from one side to the other."},{"time":566000,"text":"And as you come from the north, it is all masonry growing out of the sand cliffs"},{"time":572000,"text":"as you come from the Himalayas and evoking the tradition of the fortress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578000,"text":"And then I went away for four months"},{"time":580000,"text":"and there was going to be groundbreaking."},{"time":582000,"text":"And I came back and, lo and behold, the little model I'd left behind"},{"time":585000,"text":"had been built ten times bigger for public display on site"},{"time":589000,"text":"and ... the bridge was built!"},{"time":592000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":599000,"text":"Within the working drawings!"},{"time":602000,"text":"And half a million people gathered for the celebrations;"},{"time":608000,"text":"you can see them on the site itself as the foundations are beginning."},{"time":612000,"text":"I was renamed Safdie Singh. And there it is under construction;"},{"time":617000,"text":"there are 1,800 workers at work and it will be finished in two years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622000,"text":"Back to Yad Vashem three years ago. After all this episode began,"},{"time":627000,"text":"Yad Vashem decided to rebuild completely the historic museum"},{"time":631000,"text":"because now Washington was built -- the Holocaust Museum in Washington --"},{"time":634000,"text":"and that museum is so much more comprehensive in terms of information."},{"time":639000,"text":"And Yad Vashem needs to deal with three million visitors a year at this point."},{"time":643000,"text":"They said, \"Let's rebuild the museum.\""},{"time":645000,"text":"But of course, the Sikhs might give you a job on a platter -- the Jews make it hard:"},{"time":649000,"text":"international competition, phase one, phase two, phase three."},{"time":654000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656000,"text":"And again, I felt kind of uncomfortable with the notion"},{"time":660000,"text":"that a building the size of the Washington building --"},{"time":665000,"text":"50,000 square feet -- will sit on that fragile hill"},{"time":669000,"text":"and that we will go into galleries -- rooms with doors"},{"time":673000,"text":"and sort of familiar rooms -- to tell the story of the Holocaust."},{"time":677000,"text":"And I proposed that we cut through the mountain. That was my first sketch."},{"time":682000,"text":"Just cut the whole museum through the mountain --"},{"time":684000,"text":"enter from one side of the mountain,"},{"time":686000,"text":"come out on the other side of the mountain --"},{"time":688000,"text":"and then bring light through the mountain into the chambers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692000,"text":"And here you see the model:"},{"time":695000,"text":"a reception building and some underground parking."},{"time":698000,"text":"You cross a bridge, you enter this triangular room, 60 feet high,"},{"time":704000,"text":"which cuts right into the hill"},{"time":706000,"text":"and extends right through as you go towards the north."},{"time":711000,"text":"And all of it, then, all the galleries are underground,"},{"time":714000,"text":"and you see the openings for the light."},{"time":717000,"text":"And at night, just one line of light cuts through the mountain,"},{"time":720000,"text":"which is a skylight on top of that triangle."},{"time":724000,"text":"And all the galleries,"},{"time":728000,"text":"as you move through them and so on, are below grade."},{"time":731000,"text":"And there are chambers carved in the rock --"},{"time":736000,"text":"concrete walls, stone, the natural rock when possible -- with the light shafts."},{"time":740000,"text":"This is actually a Spanish quarry, which sort of inspired"},{"time":746000,"text":"the kind of spaces that these galleries could be."},{"time":749000,"text":"And then, coming towards the north, it opens up:"},{"time":752000,"text":"it bursts out of the mountain into, again, a view of light and of the city"},{"time":758000,"text":"and of the Jerusalem hills."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763000,"text":"I'd like to conclude with a project I've been working on for two months."},{"time":768000,"text":"It's the headquarters for the Institute of Peace in Washington,"},{"time":774000,"text":"the U.S. Institute of Peace."},{"time":776000,"text":"The site chosen is across from the Lincoln Memorial;"},{"time":781000,"text":"you see it there directly on the Mall. It's the last building on the Mall,"},{"time":785000,"text":"on access of the Roosevelt Bridge that comes in from Virginia."},{"time":790000,"text":"That too was a competition, and it is something I'm just beginning to work on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":798000,"text":"But one recognized the kind of uniqueness of the site."},{"time":802000,"text":"If it were to be anywhere in Washington,"},{"time":804000,"text":"it would be an office building, a conference center,"},{"time":807000,"text":"a place for negotiating peace and so on -- all of which the building is --"},{"time":811000,"text":"but by virtue of the choice of putting it on the Mall and by the Lincoln Memorial,"},{"time":815000,"text":"this becomes the structure that is the symbol of peace on the Mall."},{"time":820000,"text":"And that was a lot of heat to deal with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825000,"text":"The first sketch recognizes that the building is many spaces --"},{"time":829000,"text":"spaces where research goes on, conference centers,"},{"time":834000,"text":"a public building because it will be a museum devoted to peacemaking --"},{"time":838000,"text":"and these are the drawings that we submitted for the competition,"},{"time":842000,"text":"the plans showing the spaces which radiate outwards from the entry."},{"time":847000,"text":"You see the structure as, in the sequence of structures on the Mall,"},{"time":851000,"text":"very transparent and inviting and looking in."},{"time":855000,"text":"And then as you enter it again, looking in all directions towards the city."},{"time":860000,"text":"And what I felt about that building is that it really was a building"},{"time":864000,"text":"that had to do with a lightness of being -- to quote Kundera --"},{"time":871000,"text":"that it had to do with whiteness,"},{"time":873000,"text":"it had to do with a certain dynamic quality and it had to do with optimism."},{"time":879000,"text":"And this is where it is; it's sort of evolving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884000,"text":"Studies for the structure of the roof,"},{"time":887000,"text":"which demands maybe new materials:"},{"time":891000,"text":"how to make it white, how to make it translucent, how to make it glowing,"},{"time":895000,"text":"how to make it not capricious."},{"time":900000,"text":"And here studying, in three dimensions,"},{"time":903000,"text":"how to give some kind, again, of order, a structure;"},{"time":909000,"text":"not something you feel you could just change"},{"time":911000,"text":"because you stop the design of that particular process."},{"time":919000,"text":"And so it goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925000,"text":"I'd like to conclude by saying something ..."},{"time":927000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":935000,"text":"I'd like to conclude by relating all of what I've said to the term \"beauty.\""},{"time":941000,"text":"And I know it is not a fashionable term these days,"},{"time":944000,"text":"and certainly not fashionable in the discourse of architectural schools,"},{"time":948000,"text":"but it seems to me that all this, in one way or the other, is a search for beauty."},{"time":954000,"text":"Beauty in the most profound sense of fit."},{"time":957000,"text":"I have a quote that I like by a morphologist, 1917,"},{"time":966000,"text":"Theodore Cook, who said, \"Beauty connotes humanity."},{"time":970000,"text":"We call a natural object beautiful because we see"},{"time":974000,"text":"that its form expresses fitness, the perfect fulfillment of function.\""},{"time":979000,"text":"Well, I would have said the perfect fulfillment of purpose."},{"time":983000,"text":"Nevertheless, beauty as the kind of fit; something that tells us"},{"time":988000,"text":"that all the forces that have to do with our natural environment"},{"time":992000,"text":"have been fulfilled -- and our human environment -- for that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996000,"text":"Twenty years ago, in a conference Richard and I were at together,"},{"time":1001000,"text":"I wrote a poem, which seems to me to still hold for me today."},{"time":1006000,"text":"\"He who seeks truth shall find beauty. He who seeks beauty shall find vanity."},{"time":1013000,"text":"He who seeks order shall find gratification."},{"time":1017000,"text":"He who seeks gratification shall be disappointed."},{"time":1021000,"text":"He who considers himself the servant of his fellow beings"},{"time":1024000,"text":"shall find the joy of self-expression. He who seeks self-expression"},{"time":1030000,"text":"shall fall into the pit of arrogance."},{"time":1032000,"text":"Arrogance is incompatible with nature."},{"time":1035000,"text":"Through nature, the nature of the universe and the nature of man,"},{"time":1038000,"text":"we shall seek truth. If we seek truth, we shall find beauty.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1042000,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}